definitions.definition: Equal to, or greater than, or capable of achieving, five times the speed of sound .
Far enough above the speed of sound as to cause significant differences in behaviour due to chemical reactions or dissociation of the air.

main_definition: ( of a speed , aviation ) Equal to, or greater than, or capable of achieving, five times the speed of sound .
